id: CMP-mission-computer
kind: component
name: Mission computer
status: draft
conformance_level: structural
level: system
description: The LLM-UAV mission manager package running on Penny Royal (Jetson Orin Nano Super 8GB). Manages the full autonomous mission lifecycle: starts ArduPlane SITL, connects via MAVLink, arms and launches the aircraft, runs the event-driven planning loop until the aircraft lands, and archives the mission log. V1.0 baseline — frozen as of git tag v1.0.
part: executor = CMP-executor
part: planner = CMP-planner
part: telemetry = CMP-telemetry
children: CMP-executor, CMP-planner, CMP-telemetry
allocated_behaviors_resolved: BHV-mission-fsm
events_scoped_here: VAL-mission-002-boundary-pattern
